{"tid":435022,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"最好的吳宇森回歸《追捕》張涵予福山雅治雙雄預告","createTime":"2017-10-14T01:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T07:42:52.000Z","uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6f28d00c34a0f3bbd2f90c317a60fa04b9d004","tid":435022,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T01:15:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lQPVXsLQiYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlQPVXsLQiYM&d=1KxBnKZzKEj1YdruahSTgYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=42f0b85b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lQPVXsLQiYM</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有喋血雙雄/辣手神探場面三成功力已經夠做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/091515_88bb936493450b978a9fd93487af6678.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F091515_88bb936493450b978a9fd93487af6678.jpeg&h=80f0f970&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31e4ca0fd908dac926caa4a7a6b3067dbce972d7","tid":435022,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T02:05:30.000Z","msg":"試映口碑麻麻<br />\n最好帶住零期望入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231ddf98756c6931ea81c4b96085bd2237cd801f","tid":435022,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T02:07:59.000Z","msg":"老嘅名導演冇乜幾個會拍得番後生時嘅激情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5d0a5d077e587a2cb1ea3279ab050869b55b1a","tid":435022,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:18:14.000Z","msg":"睇預告好濃炒冷飯味道，"},{"pid":"673ec8cb73cf067372c25fc9dd3c632f295a5519","tid":435022,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"張poster好重大陸味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f6b4bc14fa343a5538c60d0862203e0bef7766","tid":435022,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老嘅名導演冇乜幾個會拍得番後生時嘅激情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n事實<br />\n咩王晶,低智森,黃伯鳴......"},{"pid":"711e7ab3bfe906e07bafc42269739f63468c395c","tid":435022,"uid":124450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老嘅名導演冇乜幾個會拍得番後生時嘅激情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n事實<br />\n咩王晶,低智森,黃伯鳴......</blockquote><br />\n都唔係嘅 宜家許鞍華 杜sir 徐克咪一樣做得好好睇睇<br />\n<br />\n好多程度上宜家市場主導反而限制咗舊導演嘅發揮<br />\n王晶黃百鳴拍港式喜劇起家 宜家大陸人唔受佢哋先會急於轉型做一堆爛片<br />\n高智森仲慘 以前佢同許鞍華一樣係拍人文關懷 近十年喺大陸香港兩邊走點知兩邊都不討好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許鞍華呢啲就勁 識拎投資人筆錢拍自己嘅嘢<br />\n泊埋去梁文道啲文人度 <br />\n搵幾個巨星拎投資人錢拍明月幾時有呢啲本土故事<br />\n<br />\n徐克宜家都喺大陸玩電影特技玩到入魔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗其實唔係keep唔keep團火嘅問題<br />\n而係自我定位同能力嘅關係<br />\n王三日嗰啲擺明係知拍鳩屎都會有人睇<br />\n所以用炒返嚿冷飯 慳幾蚊拍嚿屎出嚟<br />\n<br />\n吳宇森我覺得幾特殊下 <br />\n佢2000年前套套都係經典嚟<br />\n拍太平輪嗰啲都可以當佢係功成名就後想玩下新嘢<br />\n如果《追捕》都唔掂咁佢分分鐘變林嶺東咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}